Recommendation feedback tracking

Usage: memory-cli feedback <COMMAND>

Commands:
  record-session   Record a recommendation session when patterns are suggested
  record-feedback  Record feedback about which recommendations were used
  stats            Show recommendation statistics
  help             Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)

Options:
  -h, --help  Print help
